s the connection between\ndangerously irrelevant deformations and slow equilibration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Aug 2018 19:46:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 5 Jan 2019 11:20:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 10 Oct 2019 10:18:23 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 29 Jun 2021 08:12:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-30"}
