th a source with a misaligned jet of\nradiation. This study reinforces the need for more systematic investigation of\nMAGNs in order to improve understanding of the radiation emission mechanisms\nand and the disparity of detection between more powerful and weaker gamma-ray\nAGNs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Aug 2018 14:33:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-20"}
